reviewText: We watch Cyrano before Dating Agency Cyrano, the drama, came out and it was a great Intro for the drama. Personally I loved the movie and the drama.

If you are a big fan of Park Shin Hye you will be dissapointed because her character plays what I would consider a minor role.  Plot IMO is very boring and I had to fast forward just to get the movie over with.

I enjoyed this movie in US
but visual resolution of the DVD was not good enough to play on my laptop, that means this DVD is like pirat one
This movie touched my emotional side a little bit like wreckit ralph played on my childhood memories. This is good stuff!
